
Compile and launch 
  Dev 
    npm run dev ../dev-config.js
  
  Prod 
    npm run prod ../prod-config.js

Heroku
  runs the "start" script


Launch already compiled ssr jsx server
  Dev
    npm run server-launch ../dev-config.js

  Prod
    npm run server-launch ../prod-config.js

Launch on Internet server using online Heroku environment vars
    npm run server-prod

TESTS
  Selenium
    terminal 1:  cd /
                 npm run dev /selenium-tests/selenium-config.js

    terminal 2:  cd /selenium-tests
                 node all-selenium-tests


  Vitest
    npx vitest /test-jsx-browser               --silent

  
  Mocha
    npm run test-node

  
  Storybook
    npm run storybook


NB 
  All config files are outside of deleteRecipeMongo














